</div>They mention cross teaming issues but I see this as helping more in that regard. Now cross teaming guilds will be able to have their dark elves beat up on other dark elves.  Yet another step further from &quot;team server&quot; or the old name &quot;race war&quot; servers.<br />
<br />
The bounty system is funny, though we used to do that just arranged between players.<br />
<br />
I'm going to be attending the Guild Summit mentioned here: <a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/viewtopic.php?t=10355" target="_blank">http://www.thesafehouse.org/viewtopic.php?t=10355</a><br />
<br />
Feel free to add anything to that thread you'd like to see addressed that I might be able to bring up with the devs etc that I meet, particularly in regards to rogues but not excluding other classes.</div>
